column5: Thank you! Hope you're staying safe
Thank you so much for sharing this with me.
Thank you! You are already doing so much through self quarantine. We're all in this together
Aw I'm so sorry to hear that! I have seen people at their lowest point and I've learned not to take it personally. Keep your head up
Thanks I appreciate it!
Thank you! These comments have brought me so much warmth
Thanks so much! You're so right
Thanks so much! It helps thinking of the light at the end of the tunnel
Thank you friend! Hope you're staying safe yourself
Thank you for the kind words of encouragement! I appreciate it
Yes that is so true and helpful. I was doing mindfulness exercises a while back but kinda stopped. Might pick it up again. Thanks.
Thank you! This is definitely the worse time to be battling yourself, but I hope you can feel better yourself
Thank you for the warm words. I really appreciate it! Hope you and your loved ones are staying safe
Thanks!
Yes I plan to do something great for myself once this is over. Good luck you will make an amazing nurse!
Yes it's the same for us. We're all going through the same stress!
Thank you for this kind-hearted comment. It brought me a lot of comfort. I appreciate your warm words
Thanks!
Thank you so much!
Thank you so much! Haha I really love that song and for some reason it's what I wanted to listen to. Always brought me comfort in the game. Hope you're staying safe friend

Thank you so much! I am planning to get some vegan cheesecake haha
